resource.name: Neighborhoods
resource.description:
Geographical Information System file describing the shape of neighborhoods of Colorado Springs.
Neighborhoods are fluid and social and subject to change, or borders may be understood differently by different residents. This map is based on research done by the City's Comprehensive Planning Division.
If you have feedback on this map, or if you believe boundaries or names should be changed, we would like to know! Please contact opendata@springsgov.com
